<StringTableFile xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" xmlns:xsd="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema">
  <Name>conversations\02_poko_kohara\02_cv_poko_kohara_machinery</Name>
  <NextEntryID>1</NextEntryID>
  <EntryCount>11</EntryCount>
  <Entries>
    <Entry>
      <ID>1</ID>
      <DefaultText>The machine at the base of the pillar is in bad shape - the adra panels are warped and the copper is corroded, but it looks whole.

A high, keening sound comes from the adra.</DefaultText>
      <FemaleText />
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <ID>2</ID>
      <DefaultText>[Activate the machine.]</DefaultText>
      <FemaleText />
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <ID>3</ID>
      <DefaultText>[Examine the machine.]</DefaultText>
      <FemaleText />
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <ID>4</ID>
      <DefaultText>[Leave.]</DefaultText>
      <FemaleText />
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <ID>5</ID>
      <DefaultText>You turn the adra wheel and adjust some of the sliders.

At first, nothing happens.

Then, you feel a fluctuation in the ether. The wailing grows louder.</DefaultText>
      <FemaleText />
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <ID>8</ID>
      <DefaultText>You check the copper connections and knobs. Everything appears to be intact, but none of the essence in the pillar runs through it.

The keening grows louder.</DefaultText>
      <FemaleText />
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <ID>9</ID>
      <DefaultText>Essence moves within the adra, opening a dimension as raw and distorted as a fresh wound.

Something in that place pulls at your soul, and the distant voices cry out again.</DefaultText>
      <FemaleText />
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <ID>10</ID>
      <DefaultText>The dimension within the adra is open, tugging at your soul.</DefaultText>
      <FemaleText />
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <ID>11</ID>
      <DefaultText>[Project your party into the pillar.]</DefaultText>
      <FemaleText />
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <ID>12</ID>
      <DefaultText>[Project yourself into the pillar.]</DefaultText>
      <FemaleText />
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <ID>13</ID>
      <DefaultText>[Stay for now.]</DefaultText>
      <FemaleText />
    </Entry>
  </Entries>
</StringTableFile>